{"tid":2009609,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德情報局揭秘：習近平親自要求譚德塞壓下疫情訊息","createTime":"2020-05-10T01:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T15:48:11.000Z","uid":89543,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"38d9990b3e2bfd06e5e2be140f469b9f3d8947d9","tid":2009609,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:00:10.000Z","msg":"2020-05-09 08:53:36<br />\n〔中央社〕國際追究武漢肺炎疫情責任的聲浪不斷，德國情報單位指出，中國國家主席習近平親自要求世衛秘書長譚德塞淡化疫情的嚴重性，中國的隱匿造成全球至少損失一個月的時間抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n最新一期「明鏡周刊」（Der Spiegel）報導，根據德國聯邦情報局（BND）情資，中國國家主席習近平1月21日與世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）通話時，要求世衛不要發布病毒人傳人的訊息和延後全球大流行的警告。<br />\n<br />\n結果世衛沈默多天，直到1月底才宣布2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）是「國際關注的公共衛生緊急事件」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，西方國家普遍認為，如果不是中國隱瞞訊息，疫情會容易控制得多，德國聯邦情報局的結論是由於北京封鎖消息，全球平白損失4到6個禮拜的時間對抗病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3159919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3159919&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2Ffpb%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=2837d223\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3159919&h=443b36b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3159919</a>"},{"pid":"a171959c831b695ce4cece50520a1a31c7ac0c5a","tid":2009609,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7f4fcf833479599dcec34ee548d9a3efc15938","tid":2009609,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"愈來愈多料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffe159c63a7607fd95afe34269b3e1ed74d8fc4","tid":2009609,"uid":213037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線手足整咗個網站出嚟比大家做task<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgm